body.p: The following Scandinavians bought or sold real estate in Chicago recently:
Axel W. Ostrand to Henry Palmer: Robey Street [now Damen Avenue] and Berwyn Avenue. Price, $8,000.
Charles M. Storey to Nils P. Wickstrom: Southport Avenue and Grace Street. Price, $8,600.
Nils Wickstrom to Charles M. Storey: Southport and Newport Avenues. Price, $14,000.
